eded with no class. \\n\\nI’m weighing whether it’s better to assert that no class exists due to the help option instead of relying on compiling. Would `-proc:none` be more natural? I'll stick with the usual successful compile for clarity.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_WfNGr5q8K9F2IOR98Za2Ch0E|fc_089492658642b3cd0169efee198d848190aa120419b890218c", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "awk 'length($0)>120 {print FNR \":\" length($0) \":\" $0}' tests/src/ant/ant/1.6/src/test/java/ant/ant/Javac13Test.java"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 418, "output": 475, "cacheRead": 40960, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 41853, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777331726955, "responseId": "resp_089492658642b3cd0169efee0f86e08190a5466eede197a451"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_WfNGr5q8K9F2IOR98Za2Ch0E|fc_089492658642b3cd0169efee198d848190aa120419b890218c", "toolName": "bash", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "27:131:        Files.write(sourceDirectory.resolve(\"GeneratedGreeting.java\"), generatedGreetingSource().getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8));\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777331738126}]}
